Resource Profile: VitalSigns BloodGlucose

Official URL: http://nictiz.nl/fhir/StructureDefinition/vitalsign-bloodglucose Version: 1.3.15
Active as of 2023-10-17 Computable Name: Vital Signs BloodGlucose

Copyright/Legal: CC0

This profile represents a single blood glucose self measurement based on the seven-point scale (SMBG).

Usage:

  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Observation/vitalsigns-bloodglucose-01
